description:
This is a 31 minute workout called '25 Minute Full body Dumbbell Strength Workout [With Modifications / Iso Holds]' from the channel Juice & Toya.
The workout falls under Strength/Weight workout.
It's suitable for Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Disciplined Grind and The Progression Quest vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Tap in with us for a 30 minute full body strength session that's made for all levels of fitness! This workout combines basic strength training movements with isometric holds to help maximize output with each exercise. We recommend going slightly heavier in weights/dumbbells than what you may be used to in other workouts. Some of the exercises may be slightly difficult, so you can follow Juice for any of the modifications we've included. As you do this workout over time, you'll notice an improvement in your strength, ,muscle mass, and stability. Tap in to this one and let us know how you did! ðŸ”¥
